{"tid":316242,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2018 DSE 中文科 Whatsapp討論群組","createTime":"2017-07-10T14:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T06:08:22.000Z","uid":70024,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c549e92652c1abdc1dfa4223c79dca3dbdd8c057","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係J Sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以往幾年我都有響高登出沒，解答大家中文問題。今年我將會轉移陣地，黎到連登插旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n首先就開返個群組比大家喺入面問下問題先啦！<br />\n<br />\n入Group填Form：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdjLaTGkGQ-eokUIrwWpcJAGaUIqNmnrnIg2asWCpkHP6cshQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdjLaTGkGQ-eokUIrwWpcJAGaUIqNmnrnIg2asWCpkHP6cshQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=iCT20ADNahQx85AIReXcu49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fddebb27\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdjLaTGkGQ-eokUIrwWpcJAGaUIqNmnrnIg2asWCpkHP6cshQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以隨意響呢個Group問有關DSE中文科既問題，我會盡量每2-3日清一次大家既疑問。當然，大家亦可以同Group入面其他同學作學術討論。不過，討論既時候，希望大家能夠注意以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 請勿討論其他學科問題</span><br />\n話明係DSE中文Group，我相信入得黎既同學大部份都係想討論中文科既問題，因此麻煩大家唔好離題討論其他科喇！如果想討論其他科，連登會有其他Group可以比大家Join，大家自己上去搵下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 嚴禁作任何補習宣傳</span><br />\n我相信入得黎呢個Group既朋友，除左應屆考生之外，應該都有不少行家。我唔介意大家一齊幫手答問題，但請唔好響呢度宣傳任何補習課程。因為，我亦相信唔少同學會對此反感。如果你地真係響呢個Group吸引到同學PM你地，搵你地補習既話，咁我當然唔會反對啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 可以閒聊幾句，但要適可而止</span><br />\n以往我都Hold過唔少呢d研習Group，好多時同學們傾傾下就會越黎越興奮，離題萬丈，講東講西。我唔介意大家閒聊幾句，但萬一太過份既話，就會變成洗板，影響其他淨係想專心學中文既同學。所以大家要傾計就最好一句起、兩句止，或者另外再開過個Group，唔好打擾到其他同學喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 嚴禁作任何謾罵或人身攻擊</span><br />\n學術討論有時都會造成衝突。因此，希望大家理性、心平氣和咁討論，唔好鬧交。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">5. 請集中討論 DSE 相關話題</span><br />\n話明係DSE Group，就傾返DSE相關既問題，盡量唔好離題啦。(例如：有同學試過問我點樣作詩、點樣填詞等等&hellip;&hellip;老實講我未必乜都識，呢個Group既同學亦未必乜都想知，係咪？)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好喇，講左咁耐廢話，咁我又有d咩可以提供比大家呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">1 不定期文言小練習<br />\n2 不定期作文題目<br />\n3 不定期應試技巧分享<br />\n4 文憑試中文科最新資訊</span><br />\n<br />\n請恕我將以上既「服務」都set做不定期，因為小弟本身都有正職，唔可以應承大家定期會出到貨。之不過，如果大家有咩問題，我都會盡量響兩三日之內答到大家！🙏<br />\n<br />\n希望呢個Group可以幫到大家考2018 DSE啦！"},{"pid":"2425704e910fec5428ec9380dadf333bcdf868af","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179f2eee58205a9ff6c3ef89343a2b077fd39710","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62efa7eac2e3c6fe508e8a3426252f838c92f1fc","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7516dbf5f0ffce1bcfc7a5f55f16f16f9357dce5","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f4adac18e16d367349614ad4b4314594634deb","tid":316242,"uid":70024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply